West African Leaders Rescind Sanctions Against Niger After 2009 Suspension

-- B y   D j i b r i l   S a i d o u
-- 
2011-03-24T23:04:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/west-african-leaders-rescind-sanctions-against-niger-after-2009-suspension.html
West African leaders today
rescinded sanctions against  Niger , which was suspended in
October 2009.  The Economic Community of West African States decided to
reinstate Niger after “free and democratic” elections,
according to an e-mailed statement sent by the organization.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeran Wittenstein at 
 jwittenstei1@bloomberg.net  